2009-05-15 Jing Liu <jingliu@mppmu.mpg.de>
	* benchmarks/mcmc:
	  - mv benchmark.c SamplingTest1D.cc
	  - added pol0-2,exp,gaus functions to SamplingTest1D.cc
	  - changed include style in source files so that they can be compiled
	  - use BATINSTALLDIR to set -L -I directories in Makefile
	  - corrected x2 calculation in src/BCBenchmarkMCMC.cxx
	  - plot x2 to output eps in src/BCBenchmarkMCMC.cxx

